description:
My gratitude.
It is one of the shortest and darkest days of the year. I went to the delivery company office and received the parcel with new polaroid cassettes. I was thinking I can stay alive till spring now. I feel grateful to all primary collectors of Polaroid Diary, because I can buy the film and cassettes this year. I decided to make a grateful Polaroid entry, and took a picture of the bicycle in the snow.
